Hey all,

I am working on writing a functional test to have something more robust for this.

Patch Set 2:

Agree, to write a functional test where we can't mock the upload mechanism seems a bit tricky to me. Ideally, we should not use a large file to do the upload and the tests do use a fake request.

It seems to best to use unit tests for now and look for a better test structure later.
